  <para style="mt">Mikiyas</para>
  <para style="is">Igpewun-a</para>
  <para style="ip">Nekeglegse si prupita Mikiyas wey si prupita Isayas, wey migpuun sikandin te sabeka ne lungsud te Huda, ka migharian diye te igkakawanan ne balabahan dapit te igsile. Migpalintutuu amana sikandin ne ka Huda mahaan e degma egpakasalerep te iling ded ne karereetan ne impanagne ni Amus meyitenged te migharian te igkahibang ne balabahan dapit te igsile. Eglegparan te Magbebaye ne Manama ka me keet-etawan tenged te egpakapabelu ne me himu ran, ne ware nekeikul te matareng ne peggukum. Piru, ka guhuren ni prupita Mikiyas mig-uyan te klaru ne me palinneu meyitenged te egkapallateng keureme.</para>
  <para style="ip">Ka me baad te seini ne baseen ne eleg ne egsumsumanen iyan ka: ka pegpataha te meupiya ne peg-ugpe te intiru ne kalibutan ne iyan egmandu ka Magbebaye ne Manama (4:1-4), ka panagne meyitenged te sabeka ne mabantug ne Hari ne egpuun te kabuhalan ni Dabid wey eg-uyan te keupianan te nasud (5:2-5a); wey ka nasaamul te me guhuren te me prupita te Israil: “Ka intetaharan te Magbebaye ne Manama diye te keykew sika se peggimu te meupiya, ka pegpapitew layun te peggeyinawa, wey ka layun ne pegpariralem diye te Magbebaye ne Manama” (6:8)</para>
  <para style="iot">Ka nenasulat te seini ne baseen</para>
  <para style="io1">Ka peggukum te Israil wey te Huda 1:1-3:-12</para>
  <para style="io1">Ka pegpalibed wey ka meupiya ne peg-ugpe 4:1-5:15</para>
  <para style="io1">Ka guhuren te pegpaney-paney wey pegpallateng 6:1-7:20</para>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" />
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1: a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">2Har 15:32-38; 2Kru 27:1-7; </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">2Har 16:1-20; 2Kru 28:1-27; </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">2Har 18:1—20:21; 2Kru 29:1—32:33.</char>
    </note> Te me timpu ne mighari ensi Jutam, si Ahas wey si Isikiyas diye te Huda, migginguma ka lalag te Magbebaye ne Manama ki prupita Mikiyas ne matig-Musirit meyitenged te Samariya wey te Hirusalim. NEW <note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:1: a </char><char style="xt" closed="false">2Har 15:32-38; 2Kru 27:1-7; </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">2Har 16:1-20; 2Kru 28:1-27; </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false">2Har 18:1—20:21; 2Kru 29:1—32:33.</char></note> Seini ka lalag te Magbebaye ne Manama diye ki prupita Mikiyas ne matig-Musirit te timpu ne iyan mighari ensi Hutam, si Ahas wey si Isikiyas diye te Huda. Ka impakita te Manama kandin meyitenged seini te Samariya wey te Hirusalim.</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peglungku te Samariya wey te Hirusalim</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" />Palundinehan kew ka langun ne keet-etawan,</para>
  <para style="q2">pammineg kew, ka tane, wey ka langun ne mig-ugpe kayi!</para>
  <para style="q1">Ka Magbebaye ne Manama ka egpamalehet</para>
  <para style="q2">puun te matulus ne timplu rin.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Pammineg kew ka langun ne keet-etawan,</para>
  <para style="q2">pammineg kew keet-etawan te ampew te tane, sikaniyu langun se mig-ugpe te inged!</para>
  <para style="q1">Pammineha niyu ka igbennal te Magbebaye ne Manama kaniyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">Diye de sikandin te matulus ne trunu rin ka eglalag.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Pitew kew! Ka Magbebaye ne Manama egginguma puun te matulus ne ugpaanan din,</para>
  <para style="q1">egpamaneug sikandin ne diye egbaye te iddus te me bubungan.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Pammineg kew! Eglihawang ka Magbebaye ne Manama te matulus ne ugpaan din,</para>
  <para style="q1">egpamaneug sikandin wey diye egpandiek-diek te dayuwan<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Me matikang ne inged.</char></note> ne me inged te kalibutan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Egkengatunew ka me bubungan ne egdiekan din wey ka bangalug egmekegsuwey,</para>
  <para style="q2">hendue te taru ne egnakaralap te hapuy, wey hendue te weyig ne egtulayas diye te me tuhal. /NEW Egkengaleney ka me bubungan ne egdiekan din wey egkengaperi ka me napu.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egpekeiling seini te taru ne egkaralap te hapuy, wey hendue te weyig ne egtulayas diye te dalayap.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" />Egkeyitabu seini langun diye te keet-etawan te Israil</para>
  <para style="q2">su nakasale wey nakasupak sikandan te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="q1">Hentew naa ka egkabayungan te pegsupak te keet-etawan te Israil?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kene naa ne ka Samariya, ka iney ne siyudad?</para>
  <para style="q1">Hentew naa ka egkabayungan te pegsimba te kene ne mallehet ne manama te me matig Huda?</para>
  <para style="q2">Kene naa ne ka Hirusalim?</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egkeyitabu seini langun tenged te me seyyup ni Hakub,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey tenged te me sale te kabuhalan ni Israil.</para>
  <para style="q1">Hentew bes ka egpuunan ne nakasale ka Israil?<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Hakub.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">Kene naa ne ka Samariya?</para>
  <para style="q1">Hendei naa ka inged ne panubaran te me diyus-diyus diye te Huda?<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Matikang ne me inged.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">Kene naa ne ka Hirusalim?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Sikan naa ka migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Egguhusen ku ka Samariya wey kenad e seini egkeugpaan, ne egkeyimu naan de seini ne pamulaanan te me paras.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne egpanliliren ku diye te me bangalug ka me batu ne in-alad</para>
  <para style="q2">taman te egkiteen e ka me pabunsuranan kayi.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Sikan naa ka migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Egguhusen ku ka Samariya. Egkatamtamanan seini egkahuhus taman te egkeyimu e ne lebuntud ne tane,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egkapamulaan e te me paras.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne egpanliliren ku ka me batu diye te bangalug</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egguhusen ku ka me pabunsuranan kayi.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Ware bunbun ka me pabunsuranan din.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Egpanlupeten ku ka langun ne kene ne mallehet ne manama ran,</para>
  <para style="q2">egpanilaban ku ka langun ne naseleppi te me malitan ne migpamelegye te lawa ran diye te timplu,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ka langun ne me inetew-etew ran egmemakales-ag e wey egkeyimu e ne warad karuan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Naangken din seini pinaahi te me malitan ne migmamelegye te me lawa ran,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey kuntee eggamiten e degma seini te me kuntere dan</para>
  <para style="q2">eyew iyan e degma igbayad te me malitan diye te kandan ne migmamelegye te lawa ran.”</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egkengalupet ka langun ne me larawan te me diyus-diyus diye.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egkengatutung ka langun ne dasag ne impamayad te nanimba diye te timplu.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne egkengareetan e ka me diyus-diyus,</para>
  <para style="q1">su impamayad seini te me malitan ne egmamelegye te me lawa ran ne migmanimba te me diyus-diyus.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne egpanguyanen ded seini te me kuntere dan</para>
  <para style="q2">eyew eggamiten te mallindit ne pegsimba te diyus-diyus dan.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hiruwanen: Su eglilimud sikandin te suul puun te egpamelegye te me lawa ran, wey iglibed dan ka suul te me egpamelegye te me lawa ran.</char></note></para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Ne migkahi si Mikiyas, “Tenged kayi eglungku a wey egpalumbibigtew</para>
  <para style="q2">eggipanew a ne egpalawas wey ware sinilas te pegpapitew ne miglungku a,</para>
  <para style="q2">egderekul a ne iling te asu wey iling te asbistrus ne eglungku.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te ingglis: ostrich, asbistros te biniseye ne lalag.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne migkahi si Mikiyas, “Tenged kayi egsinehew a wey egpandalawit a.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egpalawas a ne eggipanew wey ware akeb te paa.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egpekeiling a te asu ne egteteul wey te kulihi ne egkukulehi.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Ustrits; Egpekeiling seini te dakel amana ne manuk ne bukug.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Su ka karereetan te Samariya iling te pali ne kenad e egkeulian</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egkeyitabu degma seini diye te Huda.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ka karereetan miggingume e diye te Hirusalim</para>
  <para style="q2">ne mig-ugpaan te keet-etawan ku.”</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Su ka pali te Samariya kenad e egkeulian,</para>
  <para style="q2">su eggalin degma seini diye te Huda.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne miggingume e seini minsan diye te me gumawan te keet-etawan ku,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne diye te Hirusalim.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peglusud te kuntere te Hirusalim</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />Kene niyu guhuri ka me kuntere ta ne me matig Gat meyitenged te karereetan ne egkeyitabu kanta.</para>
  <para style="q2">Kene niyu papitpitawa ne migsinehew kew.</para>
  <para style="q1">E keet-etawan te Bitliyapra<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Seini ka duma ne me lungsud ne ingkahi te birsikulu 10-14, ne iyan me lungsud ne eggun-aan eglusuri te me kuntere ke egpabulus e sikandan diye te Hirusalim.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">lilid-lilid kew te tane.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Kene niyu guhuri ka me kuntere ta ne matig-Gat meyitenged te egsahapan ta,</para>
  <para style="q2">kene kew pakita kandan ka egsinehew.</para>
  <para style="q1">E keet-etawan te Bitliyapra<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Baley te alinepung.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">lilid-lilid kew diye te alinepung te peglungku niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />E me keet-etawan te Sapir,</para>
  <para style="q2">hipanew kew duma te egpandakep kaniyu ne nalebasan wey neyilawan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ka me mahinged te Saanan egkengaaldek ne egpanlihawang te siyudad dan eyew te pegpangabang kaniyu.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ka me matig Bit-isil ne egpaninehew</para>
  <para style="q2">kene degma egpakapangabang kaniyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Me mahinged te Sapir,</para>
  <para style="q2">parakep kew wey duma kew ne nalebasan wey neyilawan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Kene kew egpanlihawang ka me mahinged te Saanan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ka pegpandalawit te me matig-Bit-isil,</para>
  <para style="q2">iyan palinneu ne kene kew e egpakaaput kandan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />Ka me mahinged te Marut egkengabantalan de due ka egtetahad te egpakabulig kandan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Su nasi e egmarani te gumawan te Hirusalim ka karereetan ne egpuun te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />“E me mahinged te Lakis,</para>
  <para style="q2">sangeni niyud te me kerumata ka me kudde,</para>
  <para style="q1">Pig-ikul niyu ma nahud ka me maddeet ne hinimuwan te me matig Israil,</para>
  <para style="q2">sikannaa ka nakasale ka matig Hirusalim.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Me keet-etawan te Lakis,</para>
  <para style="q2">sangeni niyud te me karwahi ka memeiyal ne me kudde wey pallahuy kew.</para>
  <para style="q1">In-ikul niyu ka me sale te me matig-Israil,</para>
  <para style="q2">sikaniyu ka migpanulu ne nakasale ka matig-Hirusalim.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" />Purisu, sikaniyu se me keet-etawan te Huda,</para>
  <para style="q2">panahataha kew e te lungsud te Murisitgat.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ka me hari te Israil</para>
  <para style="q2">kene egbulihan te lungsud te Aksib.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Purisu peuyan kew me keet-etawan te Huda te me dasag</para>
  <para style="q2">isip pegpanaha-taha te lungsud te Murisitgat.</para>
  <para style="q1">Kenad iya egbulihan te lungsud te Aksib</para>
  <para style="q2">ka me Hari te Israil.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" />Su egpeenduenan kew te Magbebaye ne Manama te me etew wey egpangahawen dan ka me lungsud niyu.</para>
  <para style="q2">E me keet-etawan te Marisa,</para>
  <para style="q2">ka me Hari te Israil egmangeles e diye te sulung te Adulam. /NEW Me keet-etawan te Marisa,</para>
  <para style="q2">egpabayaan kud man-e sikaniyu te kuntere niyu ne egdereet kaniyu.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne seeye se me pangulu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: bantug.</char></note> te Israil, eg-aput diye te Adulam.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" />Me keet-etawan te Huda, paabulug kew,</para>
  <para style="q2">para te me pinalangge niyu ne me anak,</para>
  <para style="q2">paabulug kew iling te tugkeling</para>
  <para style="q2">su egpanguripenen ma ka me anak niyu. NEW Me keet-etawan te Huda, tamperi niyu ka me bulbul niyu</para>
  <para style="q2">tenged te peglungku niyu te me anak niyu ne indakelan niyu te geyinawa.</para>
  <para style="q2">Paabulug kew iling te me tugkeling,</para>
  <para style="q2">su egpanguripenen e ka me anak niyu diye te mariyu ne inged.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka peglegpad te etew ne egpandeeg-deeg NEW Ka peglegpad te me usig</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />“Mekeyid-u-hid-u amana ka etew ne minsan mighibathibat migsumansuman te mareet!</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne emun ke egkapawe e,</para>
  <para style="q2">eggimuwen dan en iya ka insuman-suman dan ne mareet su kaya ran ma ne eggimuwen.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW “Mekeyid-u-hid-u ka egtamanan te me etew ne egsuman-suman te mareet, wey kene eglipereng ka egpamuhawang te kene ne meupiya.</para>
  <para style="q1">Te sikan pad egkasi-si ka kaliwaswasan eggimuwen dan en iya seini,</para>
  <para style="q2">su egkeyimu ran iya ka minsan nekey ne igkeupii ran ne eggimuwen.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" />Ke egkeupian sikandan</para>
  <para style="q2">te me pinamulaan kuen dan e, wey ke egkeupian te baley te duma, egkuen dan e. Ne ware pamilya wey ke kasangkapan ne egkasame.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Emun ke due tane ne igkeupii ran, eg-ahawen dan iya. Ne emun ke due baley ne igkeupii ran, egkuen dan man-e.</para>
  <para style="q2">Eglupihan dan ka kamuney te baley wey egpangahawen dan ka me kasangkapan din. Wey egbalabahan dan ka me etew ne egkaangey ran ka tane ne inggaat kandan ne karatuan.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Sikannaa ka migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Migplanu a ne egdereetan ku seini ne me etew, ne kene sikandan egpakaalihu kayi.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne kene kew e egpakapeggasal su warad egkeyimu niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Sikan naa ka migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Egdereetan ku seini ne me etew, wey kene iya sikandan egpakaalihu.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Kene kew egpakatangkas te me lieg niyu.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">Ne kene kew e egpakapeggasal pad iling dengan su warad egkeyimu niyu tenged te masumpit ne egkeula-ula niyu.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Su timpu seini te mareet.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Ke eggingume e ka sika ne timpu, eggimuwen te me etew ne panunggilingan ka karereetan ne neyitabu kaniyu, wey eg-ulahingen dan e seini te pegbaleybaley kaniyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne egkahi sikandan, ‘Warad e me karuan ney, su impanguwe e te Magbebaye ne Manama ka me tane ney</para>
  <para style="q2">wey intaladtalad e te me nenekeuripen kanami.’ ”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Mig-uripen kanami, me masinupaken</char></note></para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Te sika ne aldew, egbalbalayen kew te me kuntere niyu, wey eg-eparen e nikandan ka kalasayan wey peglungku niyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne egkahi, ‘Nenareetan key e natamtamani, su in-awe din e ka katenged ney te tane ney.</para>
  <para style="q2">Inkuwa rin seini kayi te kanami wey intalad-talad din e diye te me mig-uripen kanami.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Masamuk.</char></note>’ ”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" />Ne keureme warad e egkaangken niyu ne tane</para>
  <para style="q2">ke ig-uli e seini te me keet-etawan te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Sikan naa, warad e egkaangken niyu ne tane</para>
  <para style="q2">ke ig-uli e te Magbebaye ne Manama seini diye te me keet-etawan din.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Ne migkahi ka me etew,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Kene key pangguhuri meyitenged te due su kene egpekeyimu ka Magbebaye ne Manama ne egpeyilew kanami.</para>
  <para style="q2">NEW Ne migkahi ka me prupita ran,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Kene ka wali te iling due su kene key egpeyilawan te Manama.”</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Migsuman-suman ke buwa ne indilus te Magbebaye ne Manama ka keet-etawan te Israil?</para>
  <para style="q1">Kene bes naa ne mapariralemen ka Magbebaye ne Manama?</para>
  <para style="q2">Egpekeyimu bes naa sikandin te iling due?</para>
  <para style="q1">Kene bes naa ne hiimenawen sikandin diye te me matareng?</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Kahiyen nu buwa ne eglegparan</para>
  <para style="q1">ka kabuhalan ni Israil?<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: E baley ni Hakub, igkahi naan pad? </char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">Mahaan bes egkeupul ka panisingan te Magbebaye ne Manama?</para>
  <para style="q2">Egpekeyimu bes sikandin te iling due?</para>
  <para style="q1">Kene bes ne meupiya sikandin diye te me matareng?”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Ne migtabak ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Piglusuran niyu ka keet-etawan ku<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Ware pad naluhey ne migpanlusud ka keet-etawan ku ne iling te me kuntere.</char></note> iling te kuntere.</para>
  <para style="q1">Malinawen ka me etew ne migpuun te bununanan</para>
  <para style="q2">wey migsuman-suman ne mariyu e sikandan te karereetan,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru impangahawan niyu sikandan te me kumbale dan.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne migtabak ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Piru inlusuran niyu ka keet-etawan ku iling te me kuntere niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nanguli sikandan puun te bunuanan ne warad igkabantali,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey migsuman-suman ne mariyu e sikandan te karereetan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Piru inggepasan niyu sikandan wey immanluungan te me kumbale dan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Ne impepaawe niyu ka me malitan ne keet-etawan ku puun te meupiya ne me ugpaan ne me ugpaan dan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Impangawaan niyu te panalangin ku ka me anak dan te ware egkatamanan.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne indeldel niyu ka me malitan ne keet-etawan ku puun te inggeyinawaan dan ne me ugpaan dan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Imbalabahan niyu ka me anak dan ne egpakaangken te me panalangin ku kandan, ne kene dan e seini egkaangey pad.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />Sasindeg kew wey hipanew kew e su warad e keupianan te seini ne inged.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ka me sale niyu ka nakabehey te karereetan te kayi.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Taggel kew wey awe kew e su igkangilam e seini ne inged.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egdereetan e seini egpatamtamani tenged te me sale niyu ne iyan nakapamalindit kayi ne inged.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />Ke eggingume e ka me ubaten wey ka me limbungan wey egkahi,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Egguhuran ku sikaniyu ne egbaggiyu ka inumen ne egpekewubug,” Ne sikandan egkeyimu ne talagpangguhud te seini ne keet-etawan.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ke eggingume e ka ubaten wey ka talag-akal wey egkahi,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Igpasalig ku ne egkabayangan kew te binu wey te inumen ne egpekewubug,” ne iling iya rue ne prupita ka igkeupii te seini ne keet-etawan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />“Piru eglibulungen ku iya sikaniyu langun, me keet-etawan te Istrail!</para>
  <para style="q1">Eglibulungen ku ka nenahaat kaniyu</para>
  <para style="q2">ne iling te talag tameng te karniru diye te kulungan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey iling te eglibulung te me ayam diye te patabtaban.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egkeempet ka me tane niyu te me etew ne maggulub.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW “Eglibulungen ku red iya sikaniyu langun keureme, kabuhalan ni Hakub.</para>
  <para style="q1">Eglibulungen ku ka nenahaat ne matig-Israil!</para>
  <para style="q2">Eglibulungen ku sikaniyu iling te karniru diye te kulungan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey iling te eglibulungen ne me ayam.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egpekeempet kew wey egmaggulub kew iling te me ayam.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />Ka Magbebaye ne Manama ka eglukat wey eggun-a te egbayaan te me neneuripen eyew igpalihawang din puun te pegkeuripen.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egmanlihawang sikandan puun te siyudad wey egkaluwas sikandan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Iyan dan e hari ka Magbebaye ne Manama wey iyan eggun-a kandan. NEW Egderalan ka Magbebaye ne Manama wey eggun-a te egbayaan dan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egmanlingkesu sikandan ne egmanlihawang te me gumawan te siyudad wey egpakaawe e ka neneuripen.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne ka Magbebaye ne Manama ne Hari dan iyan eggun-a kandan wey egpanulu kandan te igbaye.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka pegdew-ey ni Mikiyas te me pangulu te Israil</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Ne migkahi si Mikiyas, “Sikaniyu se me pangulu te keet-etawan te Israil wey te Huda, pammineg kew!</para>
  <para style="q1">Sikaniyu ma perem ka eleg ne eggimu te matareng ne peggukum?</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne migkahi ad man-e, “Pammineg kew, me pangulu te kabuhalan ni Hakub, wey me talagmandu te Israil.</para>
  <para style="q1">Keilangan ne iyan niyu eg-ikulen ka matareng ne peggukum.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" />Piru nasi niyu man de iya igkeepes ka meupiya</para>
  <para style="q2">wey iyan niyu inggeyinawaan ka mareet.</para>
  <para style="q1">Pigluwitan niyu ne mannekal ka keet-etawan ku</para>
  <para style="q2">wey impangul-ulan niyu ka me tul-an dan.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Piru nasi niyu re iya igkeepes ka meupiya</para>
  <para style="q2">wey igkeupii niyu ka mareet.</para>
  <para style="q1">Inlundisan niyu ka keet-etawan ku,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey inkuwa niyu ka sapu dan diye te me tul-an dan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Impangeen niyu ka me sapu te keet-etawan ku,</para>
  <para style="q2">impanluwitan wey impanggepuan te me tul-an,</para>
  <para style="q1">wey impanggetad-getad niyu sikandan ne iling te ngalap ne egsubeen diye te kendiru.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Impangeen niyu ka sapu dan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey impanluwitan niyu ka laplap dan wey impanggepu niyu ka me tul-an dan,</para>
  <para style="q1">wey impanggupal-gupal niyu sikandan ne iling te ngalap ne egsubbeen.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Ne egginguma ka timpu ne egpangumew te pegpabulig te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru kene kew nikandin egbulihan.</para>
  <para style="q2">kene egtabaken ka me peg-ampu niyu su maddeet ma ka hinimuwan niyu.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne egpangananey kew red te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru kene kew egtabaken nikandin.</para>
  <para style="q2">Te sika ne timpu, kene kew e egpamminehen<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Iggeles din ka beneng din kandan. </char></note> nikandin tenged su maddeet ka hinimuwan niyu.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" />Piglimbungan ka me keet-etawan ku te me prupita</para>
  <para style="q2">ne migsaad te meupiya ne peg-ugpe te seeye se migsuul kandan,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru egginaldeken ne due gubut te seeye se kene egpakabehey.</para>
  <para style="q1">Purisu migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama te seini ne me prupita,</para>
  <para style="q1">/NEW Seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama</para>
  <para style="q2">diye te me ubaten ne me prupita ne mig-akal te me keet-etawan din,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Migsaaran niyu te keupianan seeye se egpakabehey kaniyu te egkeenen,</para>
  <para style="q1">piru in-ehetan niyu seeye se kene egpakabehey.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />“Warad igpakita ku kaniyu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hirbriyu: Kenad e egpakakita ka me prupita te panan-awun</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">wey kene kew e egpakapanagne. Tenged te miglimbungan niyu ka keet-etawan ku. Sikaniyu se me prupita, mahaan e egkeepus ka timpu niyu te pegpanagne wey marusilem ka egkapabulusan niyu.”</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Na, eggingumaan kew te marusilem,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru warad igmakita te Manama kaniyu, egmakalipereng kew piru kene kew e egmakataheinep.</para>
  <para style="q1">Eglineban e te aldew ka me prupita,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egpaddusilem e kandan ka aldew.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Egkeyilawan ka seeye se migpanagne te ubat,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egtiemen dan ka me bebe dan</para>
  <para style="q2">su kene ma egtabaken sikandan te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Egdali-dian seeye se me egmahehane wey egkeyilawan degma ka egmanagne.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne egsagpengan dan naan de langun ka be-be dan</para>
  <para style="q2">su warad tabak te Manama kandan.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Piru sikeddi mule, egkapenu te geem wey te panisingan ne egpuun te Magbebaye ne Manama</para>
  <para style="q2">wey pigdumaan te matareng ne peggukum wey kabagget te pegguhud</para>
  <para style="q2">te me sale ne neyimu te me matig-Israil.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Piru sikeddi mule, inhipenu a te Magbebaye ne Manama te Panisingan din wey te geem din,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey imbehayan a te pegbebatasan te matareng wey kabulut te pegguhud</para>
  <para style="q2">eyew egkasaparan ka me kabuhalan ni Hakub te mareet ne hinimuwan dan, wey eyew igpakapanengneng ku te matig-Israil ka me sale dan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Pamineg kew me pangulu te keet-etawan te Israil,</para>
  <para style="q2">sikaniyu se egkabelu te matareng ne peggukum wey miggimu te mareet dute meupiya.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Pammineg kew me pangulu te kabuhalan ni Hakub wey me talagmandu te kabuhalan ni Israil.</para>
  <para style="q2">Indew-ey niyu ka matareng ne peggukum wey egmareeten ka langun ne meupiya.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />Piggimu niyu ka siyudad te Magbebaye ne Manama, ka Hirusalim, ne egpuunan te pegpangimatey</para>
  <para style="q2">wey te kene ne matareng ne peggukum.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Innimu niyu ka Siyun<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ka igpasabut kayi: Siyudad te Manama.</char></note> pinaahi te pegpangimatey,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey impasasindeg niyu ka Hirusalim pinaahi te maddeet ne hinimuwan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />Ka me pangulu egdawat te heles de ne bayad te peggukum dan,</para>
  <para style="q2">iling te me talagpanubad ne egpanulu tenged te suul,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ka me prupita egpanagne tenged te selepi,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru inggamit dan ded ka ngaran te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="q1">Kahi ran, “Ware ki bes naa dumeyi te Magbebaye ne Manama?</para>
  <para style="q1">Ware egginguma ne karereetan kanta!”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Egpasuul pad ka me pangulu kayi human eggukum,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne igpaneleppi te me talagpanubad ka pegpanulu dan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egpanagne ka me prupita tenged te seleppi.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne minsan iling dan due, egsalig ded sikandan te Magbebaye ne Manama</para>
  <para style="q1">wey egkahi, “Pitawa niyu naa te duma ta ka Manama</para>
  <para style="q1">su ware karereetan ne egginguma kanta!”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:12: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Hir 26:18.</char>
    </note> Sikan naa, tenged kaniyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">egdereetan Hirusalim</para>
  <para style="q2">wey kenad e seini egkeugpaan ke kene egkeyimu naan de seini ne kamet,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egkeyimu e ne puwalas ka bubungan ne impasasindehan te timplu.” NEW Sikan naa, egdereetan ku ka Siyun tenged kaniyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egpekeiling e seini te daruwan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne egpekeiling e ka Hirusalim te natambu ne me batu te nallundus ne me baley,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egkeyimu ne mabbenes ka labuntud ne impasasindehan te timplu.”</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka peghari te Manama te intiru ne inged</para>
  <para style="r">(Isa. 2:2-4)</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Eggingumad ka aldew,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne ka bubungan ne nasasindehan te timplu te Magbebaye ne Manama</para>
  <para style="q2">egkeyimu e ne titikangi te langun ne bubungan kayi te kalibutan,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Amana ne impurtanti.</char></note> wey egsubla seini te duma ne me labuntud,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egmasulug ka egpanakereg kayi ne keet-etawan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" />Egpangendiye ka nalein-lein ne me etew wey egkahi,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Kuwa kew e, egpangendiye ki te bubungan te Magbebaye ne Manama,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Siyun bubungan te Magbebaye ne Manama</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">diye te timplu te Magbebaye ne Manama te Israil.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egpanuluen ki ni kandin diye ke nekey ka igpeyimu rin kanta,</para>
  <para style="q2">eyew egtumanen ta ka igkeupii rin.</para>
  <para style="q1">Su ka balaud igpangguhud diye te Siyun,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ka lalag te Magbebaye ne Manama igparineg diye te Hirusalim.”</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne masulug ka me etew te nalein-lein ne me nasud ka egpangendiye ne egkahi,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Kuwa kew e, egmangendiye ki te bubungan te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">diye te timplu te Manama ni Hakub.</para>
  <para style="q1">Igpanulu din kanta ka igkeupii rin ne eggimuwen ta,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey eyew egpekeikul ki te me Balaud din.</para>
  <para style="q1">Su igpangguhud ka Balaud ne egpuun diye te Siyun,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey igparineg ka lalag te Magbebaye ne Manama ne egpuun diye te Hirusalim.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:3: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Isa 2:4; Huw 3:10.</char>
    </note> Eggusayen din ka lein-lein ne me etew,</para>
  <para style="q2">minsan seeye se manekal ne me nasud ne diye te mariyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">Eggimuwen dan e kangkuwa ne me kampilan dan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey eggimuwen dan e ka me kalawit dan ne me ugpit.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne kenad egmabunbunuey ka me nasud, wey kenad egbebasbas sikandan para te pegbubunu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:4: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Sak 3:10.</char>
    </note> Ka tagse etew egpinpinnuu hangkuwa</para>
  <para style="q2">diye te egdalungan te pinamulaan din te paras wey te me kayu ne igira,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey warad e igkaliyasi ran.</para>
  <para style="q1">Seini ka saad te Amana ne Maresen ne Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Egpinnuu me tagse etew kangkuwa</para>
  <para style="q2">diye te egdalungan te pinamula rin ne paras wey diye te egdalungan te kayu rin ne igira,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey warad egginalat kandan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Sika ka saad te Amana ne Maresen ne Magbebaye.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" />Ka duma ne me nasud egsimba te kandan ne me manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru sikanta mule iyan ta egsimbeen ka Magbebaye ne Manama ta te ware egtamanan. NEW Ne minsan egsimba ka langun ne nasud te ngaran te diyus-diyus dan,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru egsimba ki mule te ngaran te Magbebaye ne Manama ne iyan Manama ta te ware egtamanan.</para>
  <para style="s">Ka pegpanguli te matig-Israil puun te pegkeuripen</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Te egginguma ne me aldew,</para>
  <para style="q2">eglibulungen ku ka seeye se me neneuripen, wey ka seeye se impanlegparan ku.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Egginguma ka aldew,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne eglibulungen ku seeye se nenapungku, wey egsabekeen ku seeye se neneuripen diye te mariyu, wey seeye se impanlegparan ku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Eggimuwen ku ne maddesen ne me nasud</para>
  <para style="q2">ka nenaggaat ne me luyeg wey indeeg-deeg.</para>
  <para style="q1">Sikeddiey ka eghari kandan diye te bubungan te Siyun te ware egtamanan.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Eg-uyahen ku red ka me lepu,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey eggimuwen ku seeye se neneuripen diye te mariyu ne maddesen ne me nasud.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne iyan egmandu kandan ka Magbebaye ne Manama diye te bubungan te Siyun, puun te seeye ne aldew taman te ware egtamanan.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Ne sikeykew, Hirusalim, egkeyimu kad e man e ne iney ne siyudad.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne eg-ugpe due te keykew ka Magbebaye ne Manama, iling te talagtameng te me karniru,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne egtetameng te keet-etawan din.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne sikeykew se matikang ne bakalag ne eg-ugpaan te talagtameng te punduk,</para>
  <para style="q1">ka bubungan te Siyun, eglibed ded ka katenged nu dengan,</para>
  <para style="q2">ka katenged ne eleg te Hirusalim.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Anak ne malitan te Siyun.</char></note>”</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Purisu mania te migpanamantaman ka migsinehew?</para>
  <para style="q1">Ware bes naa mighari keykew?</para>
  <para style="q1">Nenammatey bes naan e ka me talagtambag keykew</para>
  <para style="q2">su mania te migbalbaleyi ka te masakit ne iling te malitan ne egbaletikan?</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Purisu mania te migpanaman-taman ka migsinehew?</para>
  <para style="q1">Ware bes e Hari nu?</para>
  <para style="q1">Nekeiling kad te malitan ne egbaletikan ne egpakabalbaleey te masakit</para>
  <para style="q2">su namatey e ka talagtambag nu?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />Ne, gulgulibid ka tenged te masakit</para>
  <para style="q2">wey deg-uy kew keet-etawan te Hirusalim,</para>
  <para style="q2">iling te malitan ne egbaletikan su kuntee egpandelrelen kew e,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey diye kew e egmekeugpe te me kamet,</para>
  <para style="q1">egpandakepen kew wey igmeendiye kew te Babilunya</para>
  <para style="q2">piru egluwasen ku sikaniyu puun te belad te me kuntere niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne, gulgulibid ka tenged te masakit</para>
  <para style="q2">wey deg-uy ka anak te Siyun,</para>
  <para style="q2">iling te malitan ne egbaletikan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Tenged su igpalihawang kad kuntee te seini ne siyudad, eyew diye kad e egpekeugpe te unayan,</para>
  <para style="q1">wey egpehesen ka eg-uyana diye te Babilunya.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne diye, egluwasen ka te Magbebaye ne Manama puun te me kuntere nu.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Belad te me kuntere nu.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />Kuntee masulug ka me nasud ne migsabeka eyew egpakig-ehet kaniyu</para>
  <para style="q2">wey migkahi, “Egguhusen ta ka Hirusalim.”</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne kuntee masulug ka me etew te nalein-lein ne me nasud ne migsabeka eyew egpakig-ehet keykew.</para>
  <para style="q2">Migkahi sikandan, “Eglinditan ta ka Siyun, wey egtengtengan ta ka egkeyingumaan din.”</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />Piru ware nakanengneng sikandan te suman-suman te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">ware sikandan nakasabut te planu rin.</para>
  <para style="q2">Eglibulungen din bes de sikandan eyew egdusaan iling te ginalab ne trigu ne eglibulungen diye te saleg<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Innimu puun te batu ka seeg te saleg dan, wey ayam ka egdiriek kayi.</char></note> eyew egdieken.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Keet-etawan te Hirusalim, hipanew kew e wey paruseyi niyu ka me kuntere niyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">eggimuwen ku sikaniyu ne iling te me mannekal ne lukesan ne baka ne iyan sungey se putew wey iyan sulu se burunsi.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egpangguhusen niyu ka masulug ne me nasud,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egpanguyanen niyu kayi te keddi ka me karatuan dan ne naangken dan pinaahi te mareet ne paahi, wey eg-uyan niyu kayi te keddi, isip Magbebaye ne Manama te intiru ne inged.” NEW “Sasindeg ka wey diriek ka Hirusalim,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Anak te Siyun.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">eggimuwen ku sikeykew ne iling te turu ne baka ne putew ka sungey wey burunsi ka sulu.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egpanlupeten nu ka masulug ne nasud,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey igbehey nu diye te Magbebaye ne Manama ka me karatuan ne egkaangey nu kandan. Ighalad nu ka me karatuan dan kayi te keddi ne Magbebaye ne Manama te intiru ne inged.”</para>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Pangandam kew keet-etawan te Hirusalim, andama niyu ka kaniyu ne me sundalu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5.1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Kenen klaru</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">su nalingutan kid e te me kuntere ta.</para>
  <para style="q1">Impanlusuran dan e ka me pangulu te Israil. NEW Ne kuntee libulung kew ka me sundalu te siyudad</para>
  <para style="q2">su nalingutan kid e te me kuntere ta.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egbarasan dan te tuked ka beneng te pangulu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Talaggukum.</char></note> te Israil.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka insaad te Manama ne pangulu ne egpuun te Bitlihim</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:2: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Mat 2:6; Huw 7:42.</char>
    </note> Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Sikeykew Bitlihim ne nasakup te Iprata,</para>
  <para style="q2">minsan sikeykew ka tantu ne deisek ne lungsud te Huda,</para>
  <para style="q1">due egpuun te keykew ka egkeyimu ne hari te Israil,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne ka kaap-apuan din migpuun pad te me mabantug ne me etew te dengan ne timpu.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW <note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:2: </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Mat 2:6; Huw 7:42.</char></note> “Ka Bitlihim ne nasakup te Iprata,</para>
  <para style="q2">ka amana ne deisek ne lungsud te kabuhalan ni Huda,</para>
  <para style="q1">su diye egpuun ka egpangulu te Israil.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne ka migpuunan din puun pad te dengan, aney e iya dengan.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Sikannaa eg-engkeran te Magbebaye ne Manama ka keet-etawan din</para>
  <para style="q2">taman te eglesutan e ka malitan ne naberes.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne egpaliberen e ka langun ne me karumaan din puun te pegkeuripen.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Sikan naa, egbalaharen din ka matig-Israil diye te me kuntere dan</para>
  <para style="q2">taman te timpu ne eglesutan e ka malitan te ingkaberes din.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egkataman, ka me kabuhalan ni Israil ne neneuripen, igpalibed din e diye te me karumaan dan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Emun ke eglepew e sikandin, sikandin e ka egmandu te keet-etawan ne egdumaan te geem ne egpuun te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey te pegkatalahuren te Magbebaye ne Manama rin.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egpanguugpe ne mariyu te karereetan ka keet-etawan din,</para>
  <para style="q2">su ka lagun ne etew te intiru ne inged</para>
  <para style="q2">eg-ila man-e te kandin ne pegkamaresen</para>
  <para style="q2">NEW Emun ke eglepew e sikandin, egmanduan din ka keet-etawan din pinaahi te karesen te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="q2">Su diye te kandin ka katelesan te ngaran te Magbebaye ne Manama ne Manama rin.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egpanguugpe ka keet-etawan din ne warad igkabantali,</para>
  <para style="q2">su eg-ileen te intiru ne inged<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Katamanan te kalibutan.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">ka kabantug din.</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="5" style="v" />wey te kandin ne pegmandu egmalinawen ka langun. NEW Ne sikandin ka egpuunan te keupianan. Emun ke eglusuran te matig-Asirya ka inged ta wey eg-ahawen ka tane ta, eg-andaman ta sikandan te pitu ne Hari<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Talagtameng te karniru.</char></note> ne egbantey kanta wey walu ne pangulu te me etew eyew igpakuntere ta kandan.</para>
  <para style="s">Ka kaluwasan wey ka peglegpad</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Ne egkaahew ran ka Asiriya wey ka tane ni Nimrud pinaahi te kampilan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Sikandan ka egluwas kanta</para>
  <para style="q2">ke eglusuran ki te me matig-Asiriya.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW <note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:6: </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Hin 10:8-11.</char></note> Ne egkasakup dan ka tane te Asiriya pinaahi te kampilan, wey egseleran dan ka tane ni Nimrud pinaahi te kampilan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Sikandan ka egpangabang kanta puun te matig-Asiriya</para>
  <para style="q2">ke eglusuran dan ka inged ta wey ke egseleran dan ka eletanan te tane ta.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Ne ka seeye se nenakaantus ne keet-etawan te Israil</para>
  <para style="q2">egmemekegsuwey-suwey ne egmakalemung te nalein-lein ne me etew</para>
  <para style="q2">egpekeiling te dummug ne impe-uyan te Magbebaye ne Manama para te intiru ne inged</para>
  <para style="q2">wey iling te egbilisbilis ne egkengeulug diye me hilamunen.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne egkataman egpamakey e sikandan te Magbebaye ne Manama wey kenad e ne diye te etew.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne egmakalemung seeye se nenasame ne kabuhalan ni Hakub</para>
  <para style="q2">diye te nalein-lein ne me etew.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egpekeiling sikandan te demmug ne migpuun diye te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey iling te uran ne migtubi te hilamunen.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne ware sikandan migtetahad te etew wey ke diye naa te me anak te me etew.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Ka duma ne nenasame ne keet-etawan te Israil</para>
  <para style="q2">ne nekegsuweysuwey diye te naleinlein ne inged</para>
  <para style="q2">egmekeiling te liyun ne nakalemung te me mananap diye te puwalas,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ke anak naa te liyun ne diye te taliware te me karniru.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne egpandiekdiek wey egbintengbinteng kandan ne ware egpakapangabang kandan.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne egmakalemung seeye se nenasame ne kabuhalan ni Hakub</para>
  <para style="q2">diye te nalein-lein ne me nasud.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egmekeiling sikandan te liyun ne nakalemung te me mahintalunan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ke anak naa te liyun ne diye nakasewug-sewug te me punduk te karniru.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne egdidiekan wey egbinbintengen sikandan ke egpakaseled diye wey ware egpakapangabang kandan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Egkatalu te Israil ka me kuntere din,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egdereetan din sikandan langun.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Egpanalu ka keet-etawan te Israil<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:9 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Egkakayew ka belad nu.</char></note> te me kuntere dan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egguleen dan langun ka me in-ehetan dan.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama:</para>
  <para style="q2">“Te seeye ne me timpu, egpangimatayan ku ka me kudde</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egpandereetan ku ka me karwahi niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">/NEW Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Te seeye ne timpu, egpangimatayan ku ka me kudde niyu diye te taliware niyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egpandereetan ku ka me kerumata niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />Egguhusen ku ka me siyudad niyu</para>
  <para style="q2">wey eg-aminen ku te egtempag ka alad</para>
  <para style="q1">ne in-elet niyu. NEW Egguhusen ku ka me siyudad niyu diye te inged niyu</para>
  <para style="q2">wey eg-aminen ku te egguhus ka langun ne malig-en ne me alad niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />Egpangaween ku ka kaniyu ne pegkatahalambusen,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egkenga-awe ka me manenagne niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egpangaween ku ka me lambus puun kaniyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egdereetan ku ka me manenagne niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />Egpanggebeen ku ka me inetew-etew re ne manama niyu wey ka me batu ne ubag kun matulus ne impasasindeg niyu</para>
  <para style="q2">eyew kene kew e egpamakey te manama ne impangimu niyu re.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egguhusen ku ka me diyus-diyus niyu wey ka me pes-ek ne in-isip niyu ne dayuwan,</para>
  <para style="q2">eyew kene kew e egpamakey te minsan nekey ne hinimu re te me belad niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" />Egpameleren ku ka me inetew-etew te manama niyu ne si Asira</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egguhusen ku ka me siyudad niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egbaruten ku ka diyus-diyus niyu ne si Asira</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egguhusen ku ka me siyudad niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" />Ne tenged te egmangebel-ebel ne langet ku,</para>
  <para style="q2">igpaneem-neem ku pegparusa ku te me nasud ne ware migtuman keddi.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Igbusbus ku ka peglegpad ku diye te me nasud ne kene egpammineg keddi.</char></note>”</para>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka pegkasilag te Manama te Israil</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Pamineha nu ka iglalag te Magbebaye ne Manama diye te Israil.</para>
  <para style="q1">E Magbebaye ne Manama, ipanengneng nu ka pegkabelu nu diye te kabubunganan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey pangguhuri nu ka me nangumkumbetul!</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Pamineha niyu ka iglalag te Magbebaye ne Manama:</para>
  <para style="q1">Bukal-bukal kew, ipanengneng nu ka sumbung nu diye te kabubunganan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey tuhuti nu ne egpakarineg te laheng nu ka me tuhal.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Me labuntud.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" />Pammineg kew se me bubungan, te sumbung te Magbebaye ne Manama</para>
  <para style="q2">te kandin ne keet-etawan,</para>
  <para style="q2">sikaniyu se maddesen ne pabunsuranan te kalibutan, pammineg kew</para>
  <para style="q2">su ka Magbebaye ne Manama egpakiglalag te keet-etawan din duma te kabelu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Pammineg kew te sumbung te Magbebaye ne Manama, sikaniyu se me bubungan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey pammineg kew se maddesen ne me pabunsuranan te kalibutan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Su due sumbung te Magbebaye ne Manama meyitenged te keet-etawan din,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egpakig-apul sikandin te Israil.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Keet-etawan ku, nekey-a ka neyimu ku kaniyu?</para>
  <para style="q1">Mania te napelaan kew e keddi?</para>
  <para style="q1">Tabaka a nikaniyu!</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Migkahi sikandin,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Keet-etawan ku, nekey-a ka neyimu ku kaniyu?</para>
  <para style="q1">Nekey ka neyimu ku ne nakapabehat kaniyu?</para>
  <para style="q1">Tabaka a nikaniyu!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:4: a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Iks 12:50-51; </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Iks 4:10-16; </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Iks 15:20.</char>
    </note> Sikediey ka migluwas kaniyu puun te Ihiptu,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey puun te peg-uripen kaniyu,</para>
  <para style="q1">sikeddiey ka migsuhu ki Muwisis,</para>
  <para style="q2">ki Aarun wey ki Miryam eyew egpangulu kaniyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW <note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:4: a </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Iks 12:50-51; </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Iks 4:10-16; </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Iks 15:20.</char></note> Inluwas ku sikaniyu puun te inged ne Ihiptu,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey inlekat ku sikaniyu puun te pegkeuripen.</para>
  <para style="q1">Insuhu ku si Muwisis, si Aarun wey si Miryam due te kaniyu</para>
  <para style="q2">eyew egpangulu kaniyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:5: a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Num 22:2—24:25; </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Huswi 3:1—4:19.</char>
    </note> Tantanuri niyu me etew te Israil, ke nekey ka implanu ni Balak ne hari te Muwab,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ke nekey ka tabak ni Balaam ne anak ni Biyur,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ke nekey ka neyitabu puun te Sitim taman te Gilgal,</para>
  <para style="q2">eyew egkanengnengan niyu ka neyimu ku pegluwas kaniyu.” NEW <note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:5: a </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Num 22:2—24:25; </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Hus 3:1—4:19.</char></note> Sumsumana niyu keet-etawan ku, ke nekey ka implanu ni Balak ne Hari te Muwab,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ke nekey ka tabak ni Balaam ne anak<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Anak ne lukes.</char></note> ni Biyur,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ke nekey ka neyitabu puun te Sitim taman te Gilgal.</para>
  <para style="q2">Sumsumana niyu sika eyew egkanengnengan niyu ka neyimu ku te pegluwas kaniyu.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka igpeyimu te Magbebaye ne Manama</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Nekey ka eleg ne ighalad ku te Magbebaye ne Manama ke egsimba a kandin?</para>
  <para style="q1">Eg-uyan e naa te igpanubad ku</para>
  <para style="q2">ne me nati te baka ne sabeka ne tuig ka kabuyahi?</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Nekey-a ka eg-uyanen ney diye te tangkaan te Magbebaye ne Manama wey te pegpariralem te pegkeetew ney<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Peg-usengul.</char></note> diye te tangkaan te Manama ne diye te langit?</para>
  <para style="q1">Eg-uyan e naa te igpanubad ku ne ayam ne egtutungen</para>
  <para style="q2">ne nati te me baka ne senge tuig e?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Egkahale naa ka Magbebaye ne Manama te linibu ne me karniru</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ke migdalanag naa ne lana te ulibu te ware egtamanan?</para>
  <para style="q2">Eleg naa ne igpanubad ku ka kinakakayan ne anak ku eyew igbayad te me sale ku?</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egkahale naa ka Magbebaye ne Manama te linibu ne lukesan ne me karniru</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ka migsapiye naa ne lana te ware egtamanan?</para>
  <para style="q2">Eleg naa ne igpanubad ku ka kinakakayan ne anak ku eyew igbayad te sale ku, wey ka tahu kayi te lawa ku para te sale te gimukud ku?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Impapitew e te Magbebaye ne Manama te etew ka meupiya.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne ka igkeupii re te Magbebaye ne Manama ne</para>
  <para style="q2">eggimu kew te matareng ne peggukum, wey te peggeyinawa te meupiya,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey pariralem kew te pegsabeka niyu te Magbebaye ne Manama niyu.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Impapitew rin te etew ke nekey ka meupiya.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne nekey naa ka ingkeilangan din diye te keykew?</para>
  <para style="q2">Eg-ugpe ka ne matareng, wey meupiya ka batasan nu,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ikul ka ne mapariralemen te Manama nu.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Matagseb ka etew ne due pegkaaldek te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="q1">Purisu pammineg kew langun se me mahinged te siyudad te Hirusalim.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Pammineg kew! Migpangumew ka Magbebaye ne Manama te siyudad.</para>
  <para style="q1">Matagseb ka egkaaldek te ngaran din, “Pammineg kew, sikaniyu se me tribu ne migliblibulung te siyudad<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:9 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: E tribu, pammineg kew te tuked wey te sabeka ne migtunde kayi.</char></note>!</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />Migpanlimud kew te me tinakew niyu diye te me baley niyu</para>
  <para style="q1">wey migpanlimbung kew pinaahi te peggamit niyu te kene ne eleg ne timbangan</para>
  <para style="q2">ne seini ka amana ku igkabelu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egkalingawan ku naa ka me tinakew ne karatuan te maddeet ne me etew ne impanahu dan diye te me baley ran?</para>
  <para style="q1">Wey egbalaharen ku naa ka peggamit dan te kene ne eleg ne timbangan</para>
  <para style="q2">ne igkeepes ku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />Egpasayluwen ku naa ka etew ne miggamit te kene ne eleg ne timbangan?</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egpasayluwen ku naa ka etew ne limbungen wey eggamit te kene ne eleg ne timbangan wey ka due tahuanan din ne kene ne eleg ka kabehat?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />Sikaniyu se me datu miglupihan niyu ka me egkengaayu-ayu</para>
  <para style="q2">me ubaten kew wey me limbungen.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egpanlupig<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Napenu te kabulut.</char></note> ka meyaman ne me etew ne due te kaniyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">me ubaten ka me mahinged due wey amana egkateu kew ne egmanlimbung.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Limbungen ka dile dan diye te be-be dan.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />Purisu egdereetan ku sikaniyu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6.13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Pinaahi te dalu</char></note> tenged te me sale niyu. NEW Purisu migbunsuran kud sikaniyu te egdereet<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Egpareraluwen ku sikaniyu.</char></note>, egbalbalangan ku sikaniyu tenged te me sale niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" />Egpangekeen kew piru kene kew egkengabulung,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne nasi de iya egpekeiling te ware me tahu te getek niyu,</para>
  <para style="q1">eglilimud kew, piru ware egkalimud niyu</para>
  <para style="q2">su egpandereetan de te me kuntere niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egkeen kew piru kene kew egkabulung,</para>
  <para style="q2">ware ded man-e tahu te getek niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">Eglilimud kew, piru ware egkalimud niyu</para>
  <para style="q2">su igbehey ku ka nalimud niyu diye te kuntere<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Kampilan.</char></note> niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" />Egpamula kew piru kene kew egpakahaani,</para>
  <para style="q2">egkekeles kew te me ulibu piru kene kew egpakagihisa te eggilutuen niyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">egkekeles kew te ubas piru kene kew egpekeinum te weyig kayi.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egpamula kew piru kene kew egpakahaani,</para>
  <para style="q2">egkekeles kew te me ulibu piru kene niyu egkahamit ka lana,</para>
  <para style="q2">egkekeles kew te me ubas piru kene niyu egkeinum ka binu kayi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" />Egkeyitabu seini su miggimu kew ma te maddeet ne me himu ni Hari Umri</para>
  <para style="q2">wey te anak din ne si Hari Ahab.</para>
  <para style="q1">Impabulus niyu ka me himu ran</para>
  <para style="q2">purisu egdereetan ku sikaniyu wey ka me karatuan niyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne eglemetan kew wey egngingisiyan te keet-etawan te minsan hendei ne me inged. NEW <note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:16: a </char><char style="xt" closed="false">1Har 16:23-28; </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">1Har 16:29-34; 21:25-26.</char></note> Egkeyitabu seini su in-ikul niyu ma ka me suhu ni Hari Umri</para>
  <para style="q1">wey ka langun ne mareet ne hinimuwan te kabuhalan ni Akab,</para>
  <para style="q1">wey in-ikul niyu ka me tuluuwen dan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Purisu egdereetan ku sikaniyu wey eglemetan kew e te me mahinged due,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egngingisiyan te keet-etawan te minsan hendei ne me inged.</para>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka peglungku wey pegpangananey</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Ware karuan te langun ne neyimu ku!</para>
  <para style="q1">Su egpekeiling a te etew ne eggutasan</para>
  <para style="q2">ne egpamitew te behas te kayu ne ware nakita, wey ke behas naa te ubas ne egkeenen piru ware nasame.</para>
  <para style="q2">Su naamin e pamupuwa ka behas te ubas wey te kayu ne igira.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Mekeyid-u-hid-u a!</para>
  <para style="q1">Su egpekeiling a te etew</para>
  <para style="q2">ne migpakileew te prutas te gulabung, wey ke egpamurut naa te behas te ubas ne nasame.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne warad egkakeen ku ne pinungpung ne me ubas, wey warad ka igkeupi ku ne an-anayan ne behas te igira.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" />Ne warad etew ne migpamakey te Magbebaye ne Manama wey warad e matareng.</para>
  <para style="q1">Migtetahad ka tagse sabeka eyew te peggimatey te duma,</para>
  <para style="q2">iling te mangngasuwen ne mig-e-atang te eggingutelen din.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne warad etew ne matinumanen te Manama kayi te ampew te tane wey warad matareng ne etew ne nakasangi te me etew.</para>
  <para style="q1">Eggeepas ka langun ne etew eyew te peggimatey te duma,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne ka tagse sabeka eg-andam te baled minsan te suled din.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Ne mangngateu sikandan ne eggimu te mareet,</para>
  <para style="q2">egdawat ka me pangulu ran wey ka me talewusey te bayad<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: brayb</char></note>puun te maddeet ne me himuwan dan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ka mabantug ne etew egpangguhud te maddeet ne puhawang</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egmekegtuleduwey sikandan.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne mangngateu iya sikandan ne eggimu te mareet.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egbuyu ka me pangulu ran te me bayad, wey egdawat ka me talehusey te me suul.</para>
  <para style="q1">Sikan naa, ka mabantug ne etew egpangguhud te maddeet ne puhawang ne igkeupii rin,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egmekegtuleduwey sikandan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Ne minsan ka me kene ne ubaten wey me matareng ne me etew</para>
  <para style="q2">egkeyimu e ne ware karuan iling te sapinit.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">Miggingumee ka timpu ne elegparan<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Kew</char></note> te Magbebaye ne Manama ka me etew,</para>
  <para style="q2">sumale te impaney-paney kandan pinaahi te me talagtameng kandan, wey te me prupita.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne kuntee nenasamuk e sikandan.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Minsan seeye se meupiya diye te kandan egpekeiling te sapinit,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ka matareng iling e te alad ne duhiyen.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">Miggingume e ka aldew te peglegpad kandan</para>
  <para style="q2">sumale te impaney-paney kandan te me talagtameng dan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne kuntee nenalibeg e sikandan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" />Kene kew sahe-sahe te me sumbaley niyu wey ke me alukuy niyu naa,</para>
  <para style="q2">bantey kew te me peglalaglalag niyu minsan diye te me asawa niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Kene ka sahe-sahe te sumbaley nu, wey kene ka salig te alukuy nu naa.</para>
  <para style="q2">Kene ka pangpangguhud minsan diye te asawa nu.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Banteyi nu ka me gumawan te be-be nu puun kandin ne mig-ukembe te kumeng nu.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:6: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Mat 10:35-36; Luk 12:53.</char>
    </note> Su ka anak ne lukes egleig-leig te amey rin,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ka anak ne malitan egsukul e te iney rin,</para>
  <para style="q2">egsukul ka ambey te anuhang din ne malitan,</para>
  <para style="q2">egmegkuntereey kew ka me taltalag duma.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW <note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:6: </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Mat 10:35-36; Luk 12:53.</char></note> Ne iyan ded egkakuntere te etew ka diye mismu te baley rin.</para>
  <para style="q2">Su ka anak ne lukes eglemet te amey rin,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ka anak ne malitan eg-atu e te iney rin.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne eg-atu ka ambey te anuhang din ne malitan.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Piru egsalig a mule te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">egtetahad a te Magbebaye ne Manama ne iyan egluwas keddi,</para>
  <para style="q2">egpamineg sikandin keddi. NEW Piru sikeddi, egsalig<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Egtengteng.</char></note> a mule te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">egtetahad a te Manama ne iyan manluluwas ku.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egpaminehen a te Manama ku.</para>
  <para style="s">Ka pegluwas te Magbebaye ne Manama</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Sikaniyu se me kuntere ney,</para>
  <para style="q2">kene kew kahale tenged te natalu key nikaniyu,</para>
  <para style="q2">su minsan ke natalu key e egsasindeg key red man-e,</para>
  <para style="q1">minsan seini key kuntee te marusilem,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru ka Magbebaye ne Manama ka eglayag kanami.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Kene ka kahale,</para>
  <para style="q2">kuntere ku,</para>
  <para style="q2">su egsasindeg e red ke napeled a.</para>
  <para style="q1">Minsan diye a nakatahu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Nakapinnuu.</char></note> te marusilem,</para>
  <para style="q2">piru ka Magbebaye ne Manama ka egteng-ew keddi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Eg-antusen ney e ka langet te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">su nakasale key ma kandin,</para>
  <para style="q2">taman te egbulihan key nikandin.</para>
  <para style="q1">Igpalihawang key nikandin puun te marusilem peendiye te malayag</para>
  <para style="q1">wey egluwasen key nikandin.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Eg-antusen ku ka langet te Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">tenged su nakasale a kandin,</para>
  <para style="q2">taman te egpangabangan a nikandin wey eggukuman ad nikandin.</para>
  <para style="q1">Igpalihawang a nikandin peendiye te malayag,</para>
  <para style="q1">wey egkaneem-neem ku red ka pegluwas din keddi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />Ne egkakita seini te kuntere ney</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egkeyilawan sikandan amana,</para>
  <para style="q1">ne egkahi sikandan, “Kene egpakapangabang kaniyu ka Magbebaye ne Manama niyu.”</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne egkiteen ney ne egkatalu ka me kuntere ney wey egpandidiekan<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Egkiteen...didiekan:</char></note> ne iling te basak diye te deralanen.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Ne egkakita seini te kuntere ku</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egkeyilawan seeye se migkahi,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Na hendei naan e ka Magbebaye ne Manama ne Manama nu?”</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne kuntee egkiteen kud sikandin ne egkatalu ne egdi-diekan iling te basak diye te deralanen.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />Keet-etawan te Hirusalim,</para>
  <para style="q2">eggingumee ka timpu ne eggimuwen e eg-abayi ka me alad te siyudad niyu,</para>
  <para style="q1">wey te sika ne timpu egtimulan pad man-e ka me tane.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egginguma ka aldew ne eg-abayan e man-e te eggimu ka alad te siyudad niyu,</para>
  <para style="q1">wey egkatimulan ka kaluag te ugpaan niyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />Ne ka me karumaan niyu egmekeuli e puun te Asirya ne dapit te igsile,</para>
  <para style="q2">te Ihiptu ne dapit te kakawanan ne balabahan, te weyig te Iyupratis, wey puun te maddiyu ne me inged.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Te sikan ded ne aldew, egmangendiye keykew ka me etew ne egpuun te lein-lein ne inged,</para>
  <para style="q2">ka diye egpuun te Asirya taman te Ihiptu wey peendiye te weyig ne Iyupratis, wey ka egpuun te nekegtalipag ne me bubungan wey wey nekeglimang ne me bubungan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />Piru egkeyimu ne inged ne mammara ka tane</para>
  <para style="q2">tenged te mareet ne hinimuwan te me etew. NEW Piru egkeyimu ka kalibutan ne ware mahinged</para>
  <para style="q2">tenged te mareet ne hinimuwan te me etew.</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peg-ampu ni prupita Mikiyas para te keet-etawan te Israil NEW Ka himenew te Manama te Israil</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" />Magbebaye ne Manama, bantayi nu ka keet-etawan ne pig-alam nu.</para>
  <para style="q2">Minsan ke sikandan de ka mig-ugpe diye te inged ne ware mahinged, ne nalingutan te meupiya ne tane ne diye te puwalas te bubungan te Kamilyu.</para>
  <para style="q1">Patabtaba nu sikandan diye te Basan wey te Gilyad, iling te dengan ne timpu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Magbebaye ne Manama, bantayi nu ka keet-etawan nu ne in-alam nu, iling te pegbantey te sabeka ne talagtameng.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Pakeena nu ka keet-etawan nu pinaahi te tuked nu, ka punduk te kabuhalan nu.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">Ne migsabsabeka ne mig-ugpe diye te taliware te puwalas ne diye te meupiya ne tane.</para>
  <para style="q1">Patulena nu sikandan diye te Basan wey te Gilyad, iling te dengan ne timpu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" />Magbebaye ne Manama himuwa nu ka me kein-inuwan kayi te kanami<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Eggimu a te me kein-inuwan para kandin.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2">iling te piggimu nu te timpu te pegpalihawang nu kanami puun te Ihiptu.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW “Igpakita ku kaniyu ka me kein-inuwan,</para>
  <para style="q2">iling te innimu ku te timpu te impalihawang ku sikaniyu ka neneuripen diye te Ihiptu.”</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" />Egpakakita te seini ka me etew te duma ne inged</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egkeyilew sikandan minsan pad ke maddesen sikandan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Te pegkeyilew ran inpegtiem dan ka me be-be dan wey insagpengan ka me talinga ran.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Egkakita seini te me nasud,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne neyilawan sikandan wey naawe ka langun ne geem dan.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne egsagpengan dan naan de ka be-be dan te me belad dan wey kenad egdineg ka me talinga ran tenged te pegkeyilew ran.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" />Egmakarul-ug-dul-ug naande sikandan te tane iling te uled</para>
  <para style="q2">wey iling te me ayam ne egpananap te tane,</para>
  <para style="q1">egmanlihawang sikandan puun te me helesanan dan ne egpangelkelen tenged te pegkaaldek dan keykew te Magbebaye ne Manama ney</para>
  <para style="q2">te pegkaaldek dan egpakaparani e sikandan keykew.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">NEW Egpandile naan de sikandan te alinepung iling te uled,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey iling te me ayam ne egpananap te tane.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egpangelkelen sikandan ka eglihawang puun te me ugpaan dan, wey eglibed sikandan ne egkaaldek diye te Magbebaye ne Manama ne Manama ta,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egkaaldek sikandan ka egparani kandin.</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" />E Magbebaye ne Manama, ware egpekeiling keykew minsan sabeka</para>
  <para style="q2">ne egpakapasaylu te me sale te nenasame ne keet-etawan.</para>
  <para style="q1">Kene ka egtines te kabelu te ware egtamanan,</para>
  <para style="q2">su igkeupii nu ne igpapitew ka geyinawa nu ne ware egtamanan.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Ware duma ne manama ne egpekeiling keykew,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne egpakapasaylu te me sale te nenagaat ne keet-etawan nu wey eglingew te sale te pinalangge din?</para>
  <para style="q1">Kene ka egtahu te kabelu te ware egtamanan,</para>
  <para style="q2">su igkeupii nu ne igpapitew ka dakel ne geyinawa nu ne ware egtamanan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" />Egkeyid-u kad e man e kanami.</para>
  <para style="q2">Indidiekan nud e ka langun ne sale ney</para>
  <para style="q2">wey indegpak nu diye te kinariraleman te dahat.</para>
  <para style="q1">NEW Igkeyid-u key e man-e nikeykew.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egdi-diekan nud e ka langun ne sale ney</para>
  <para style="q2">wey indegpak nud e seini diye te pused te dahat.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" />Impapitew nu ka pegkamatinumanen nu diye ki Hakub,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey impapitew nu ka geyinawa nu ne kene egkataman diye ki Abraham,</para>
  <para style="q2">iling te insaad nu diye te kaap-apuan ney te dengan ne timpu. NEW Igpakita nu ne egtumanen nu ka saad nu diye te me kabuhalan ni Hakub,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ka geyinawa nu diye te kabuhalan ni Abraham,</para>
  <para style="q2">iling te insaad nu diye te kaap-apuan ney aney pad dengan.</para>
</usx>